<p>来自<em>非参考期刊</em>最后一期的通知卡。[归档于橱柜Yodh-12，栏号十三，盒号二]。</p>
</blockquote>
<table style="width:900px;border-collapse:collapse;padding:0px;margin:25px auto;font-size:14px;">
<tr style="background-image:url('paper.gif')">
<td style="padding:5px 15px 0px 15px;border:1px solid black; border-bottom:none; background-color:#a0a0f0; text-align:center;"><span style="font-size:200%;">通知信：最后一期</span></td>
